Run.

1248
01:36:09,169 --> 01:36:11,006
Walk past each other.

1249
01:36:11,014 --> 01:36:14,338
Chase each other.

1250
01:36:15,509 --> 01:36:18,160
Never give up on each other.

1251
01:36:19,240 --> 01:36:24,687
We are hand in hand,

1252
